snippet.title: Sonic X TMNT: Score Party // SAGE 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-x-tmnt-score-party.2134/

Sonic X TMNT: Score Party is a collection of mini-games featuring classic Sonic and teenage mutant ninja turtles from the animated show from the 80s! In these mini-games you will need to collect a certain number of points. Their total number is rated S or D rank, depending on how many points you have collected. In this demo, you will be able to run at super sonic speed as Sonic and kick some shells as Leonardo! At different levels from the games of both franchises, you will meet Dr. Eggman's badniks and Shredder's foot soldiers (and not only)!

Developed by Temate08
